            <bug_when>2009-12-07 10:31:09 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>This property can be used to make &quot;shadow&quot; and &quot;decorator&quot; elements transparent to mouse clicks. Especially for the shadows this is a huge win. Further the protector elements might not be needed if the decorator has &quot;ponter-events: none&quot;.

A further optimization could be to make &quot;anonymous&quot; widgets transparent to mouse events as well.

This feature is supported in FF 3.6 and Safari 4.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
