            <thetext>Some good use cases here.

Something for maybe qx.bom.element.Style. A method supportsStyle(name) could be useful e.g.

supportsStyle : function(name) {
  return window.getComputedStyle(document.documentElement)[&quot;pointer-events&quot;]
}

As this is not dependend on ony specific element, one parameter is enough.</thetext>
